quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,16,aur jab tum ne un ( mushrikon ) se aur jin ki yeh khuda ke siwa ibadat karte hain un se kinara karliya hai to ghaar mein chal raho tumhara perwar-digaar tumahray liye apni rehmat wasee kardey ga aur tumahray kamon mein aasani ( ke samaan ) muhayya kere ga
  18,17,aur jab Sooraj niklay to tum dekho ke ( dhoop ) un ke ghaar se dahni taraf simat jaye aur jab ghuroob ho to un se baen taraf katra jaye aur woh is ke maidan mein they. yeh khuda ki nshanyon mein se hain. jis ko khuda hadaayat day ya woh hadaayat yab hai aur jis ko gumraah kere to tum is ke liye koi dost raah bitanay wala nah pao ge
  18,18,aur tum un ko khayaal karo ke jaag rahay hain halaank woh sotay hain. aur hum un ko dayen aur baen karvat badlatay they. aur un ka kutta chokhat par dono haath phelaaye hue tha. agar tum un ko jhaank kar dekhte to peeth phair kar bhaag jatay aur un se dehshat mein aajate
  18,19,aur is terhan hum ne un ko uthaya taakay aapas mein aik dosray se daryaft karen. aik kehnay walay ne kaha ke tum ( yahan ) kitni muddat rahay? unhon ne kaha ke aik din ya is se bhi kam. unhon ne kaha ke jitni muddat tum rahay ho tumhara perwar-digaar hi is ko khoob jaanta hai. to apne mein se kisi ko yeh rupiya day kar shehar ko bhaijho woh dekhe ke nafees khana kon sa hai to is mein se khana le aeye aur aahista aahista aeye jaye aur tumhara haal kisi ko nah betaye
  18,20,agar woh tum par dustarus paleen ge to tumhe sangsar kar dein ge ya phir apne mazhab mein daakhil karlen ge aur is waqt tum kabhi Falah nahi pao ge
